OL,3,CWhy volunteering is at the heart of
OL,4,Cour communities
OL,6,FThis week marks Volunteer's Week and
OL,7,Fin Northern Ireland, volunteers form
OL,8,Fthe backbone of so many of our
OL,9,Fcharities and services. In our podcast
OL,10,F'Going the Extra Mile,' I have met
OL,11,Fwonderful, selfless people who
OL,12,Fdedicate time and effort to helping
OL,13,Fothers and this week is no exception.
OL,15,FElaine McBride has volunteered and
OL,16,Ffundraised for the Northern Ireland
OL,17,FHospice for the past nine years. Her
OL,18,Freason for doing so? Her son Sam.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
