PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1780592748
OL,3,CWhy volunteering is at the heart of
OL,4,Cour communities
OL,6,FElaine says that her personal
OL,7,Fexperience with the hospice means that
OL,8,Fshe is passionate about promoting it
OL,9,Fat every opportunity.
OL,11,FShe knows that the Hospice jostles
OL,12,Fwith so many other good causes when it
OL,13,Fcomes to fundraising and public
OL,14,Fawareness.
OL,16,FShe's set up social media groups,
OL,17,Fengaged with her local community and
OL,18,Fcarried out eye-catching challenges to
OL,19,Fraise money.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
