OL,3,CWhy volunteering is at the heart of
OL,4,Cour communities
OL,6,FAnd the next person to join her? Sam.
OL,7,FIt's been 25 years since the
OL,8,FChildren's Hospice was set up and the
OL,9,Ffamily will push Sam in his wheelchair
OL,10,Ffor 25 miles.
OL,12,FIt's a family affair and one which Sam
OL,13,Fcouldn't be happier about.
OL,15,FFor Elaine, her motivation to
OL,16,Fvolunteer is personal but she doesn't
OL,17,Fhesitate to promote the value of
OL,18,Fvolunteering for others. She speaks
OL,19,Fwith pride about the value and
OL,20,Ffriendships that it has brought to her
OL,21,Flife.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
