OL,3,CWhy volunteering is at the heart of
OL,4,Cour communities
OL,6,FFor Sam, he will no longer be eligible
OL,7,Ffor respite care in the Children's
OL,8,FHospice from next year. The family
OL,9,Fdoesn't know how much help they will
OL,10,Freceive after that but two things are
OL,11,Ffor sure....Elaine will keep
OL,12,Fvolunteering and Sam will continue to
OL,13,Fbe her little prince.
OL,15,FTo get involved with NI Hospice, you
OL,16,Fcan find more information at https:/
OL,17,F/www.nihospice.org/get-involved/
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
